n                <span><span class=\"sub\">hosting-compare.io</span> · review · 4d ago</span>\n                <span class=\"meta\" style=\"margin-left:auto; color: var(--amber)\">★ 4.1</span>\n              </div>\n              <h4>\"Cheap, but you can tell it's one guy\"</h4>\n              <p>SLA is honest at <em>99.61%</em>. Bandwidth limits weren't documented. UI is rough but actually responds to tickets.</p>\n              <div class=\"react\"><span>views <b>1.2k</b></span><span>helpful <b>17</b></span></div>\n            </div>\n          </section>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </main>\n</div>\n";
